modShortDescription: Another stack size mod for you! This 7 Days to Die mod increase stack sizes. All items will have 1000 stack size, all blocks will have 20000 stack size.
modDescription:
Another [stack size](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-stack-size/) mod for you! This 7 Days to Die mod increase stack sizes. With this mod, all items will have 1000 stack size, all blocks will have 20000 stack size.

[Download](https://botmanhosting.com/A18/HH_Larger_Stack_Size.zip)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11963-highopes-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Highope](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/highope/)
